Disclaimer

All content on the Erasmus+ Project Result Platform is provided as submitted by the (coordinating) beneficiary. The publication of projects and their results requires all users to respect the terms of use of the platform when uploading information.

Compliance with EU values and applicable personal data protection requirements and respect of pre-existing intellectual property rights and image rights falls outside the control of the European Commission and is the explicit responsibility of (coordinating) beneficiaries.

The European Commission reserves the right to temporarily or permanently remove any content that violates any of the above and/or the terms of use, to ensure compliance with the applicable rules.
